section.section:
The bonds of each issue:
Shall be dated;
Shall bear interest at a rate or method of determining rates;
Shall mature at a time not exceeding forty (40) years from their issuance date, as determined by the issuing authority; and
May be redeemable before maturity, at the option of the issuing authority, at a price and under terms and conditions as may be fixed by the issuing authority prior to the issuance of the project revenue bonds.
